trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of properties and values that are associated with an object in the <see cref="N:System.Printing" /> namespace.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de propriedades e valores associados a um objeto no namespace <see cref="N:System.Printing" />.

trans-unit.source: The collection takes the form of a <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable> dictionary.
trans-unit.target: A coleção assume a forma de um <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable> dicionário.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A> property of each <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry> in the collection is an instance of a class that is derived from <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A> propriedade de cada <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry> na coleção é uma instância de uma classe derivada de <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty>.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to use this class to install a second printer that differs in its properties from an existing printer only in location, port, and shared status.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir mostra como usar essa classe para instalar uma segunda impressora que difere em suas propriedades de uma impressora existente apenas no local, porta e status compartilhado.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to use this class to discover at run time the properties, and the types of those properties, of a print system object, without using reflection.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir mostra como usar essa classe para descobrir em tempo de execução as propriedades e os tipos dessas propriedades, de um objeto do sistema de impressão, sem o uso de reflexão.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: The data that is required to serialize or deserialize an object.
trans-unit.target: Os dados necessários para serializar ou desserializar um objeto.

trans-unit.source: The context of the serialized stream, including the source and the destination.
trans-unit.target: O contexto do fluxo serializado, incluindo a origem e o destino.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" /> class and provides it with the specified <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> and <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" />.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" /> e a fornece com o <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> e o <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" /> especificados.

trans-unit.source: An object (of a class that is derived from <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />) that represents a property of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto (de uma classe derivada de <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />) que representa uma propriedade de um componente de hardware ou software do sistema de impressão.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified object (of a class that is derived from <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />) into the dictionary.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o objeto especificado (de uma classe derivada de <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />) no dicionário.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty.Name%2A> property of `attributeValue` becomes the <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Key%2A> property of the new <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty.Name%2A> propriedade `attributeValue` se torna o <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Key%2A> propriedade do novo <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty> as a whole becomes the <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A> property of the new <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty> como um todo se torna o <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A> propriedade do novo <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>.

trans-unit.source: For another way to add an entry to the dictionary, see <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.SetProperty%2A>.
trans-unit.target: De outra maneira de adicionar uma entrada ao dicionário, consulte <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.SetProperty%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to use this method to install a second printer that differs in its properties from an existing printer only in location, port, and shared status.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir mostra como usar esse método para instalar uma segunda impressora que difere em suas propriedades de uma impressora existente apenas no local, porta e status compartilhado.

trans-unit.source: Releases the resources that are being used by the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Libera os recursos que estão sendo usados pelo <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: Releases all the resources that are being used by the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Libera todos os recursos que estão sendo usados pelo <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: Call <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> when you are finished using the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>.
trans-unit.target: Chamar <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> quando tiver terminado de usar o <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> method leaves the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> método deixa o <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> em um estado inutilizável.

trans-unit.source: After calling <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose>, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> so that the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Depois de chamar <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose>, você deve liberar todas as referências para o <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> para que o coletor de lixo possa recuperar a memória que o <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> estava ocupando.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [limpeza de recursos não gerenciados](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) e [implementar um método Dispose](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).

trans-unit.source: Always call <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>.
trans-unit.target: Sempre chamar <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> antes de liberar sua última referência para o <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources that it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method of the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> object.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, os recursos que está usando não serão liberados até que o coletor de lixo chame o <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> método o <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are being used by the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" /> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Libera os recursos não gerenciados que estão sendo usados pelo <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" /> e libera opcionalmente os recursos gerenciados.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Este método é chamado pelo método público <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> e pelo método <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> invokes the protected <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose%28System.Boolean%29> method with the unnamed Boolean parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> invoca o protegido <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose%28System.Boolean%29> método com o parâmetro booliano sem nome definido como `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose%28System.Boolean%29> with the parameter set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invoca <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose%28System.Boolean%29> com o parâmetro definido `false`.

trans-unit.source: When the Boolean parameter is `true`, this method releases all the resources that are held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> references.
trans-unit.target: Quando o parâmetro booliano é `true`, esse método libera todos os recursos que são mantidos por qualquer objeto gerenciado que este <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> referências.

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Este método invoca o método `Dispose()` de cada objeto referenciado.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="Dispose" /> can be called multiple times by other objects.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Dispose" /> pode ser chamado várias vezes por outros objetos.

trans-unit.source: When you override <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, be careful not to reference objects that have been previously disposed of in an earlier call to <see langword="Dispose" />.
trans-unit.target: Quando você substituir <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, tenha cuidado em não para referenciar objetos que têm foi descartados anteriormente em uma chamada anterior para <see langword="Dispose" />.

trans-unit.source: For more information about how to implement <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, see [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre como implementar <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, consulte [implementar um método Dispose](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).

trans-unit.source: For more information about <see langword="Dispose" /> and <see cref="M:System.Object.Finalize" />, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) and [Overriding the Finalize Method](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre <see langword="Dispose" /> e <see cref="M:System.Object.Finalize" />, consulte [limpeza de recursos não gerenciados](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) e [substituindo o método Finalize](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3).

trans-unit.source: Stores all the data that is used to serialize the object.
trans-unit.target: Armazena todos os dados usados para serializar o objeto.

trans-unit.source: Describes the context of the serialized stream, including the source and the destination.
trans-unit.target: Descreve o contexto do fluxo serializado, incluindo a origem e o destino.

trans-unit.source: Populates a <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> with the data that is needed to serialize the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Preenche um <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> com os dados necessários para serializar o <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: The name of the property that is represented by the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />.
trans-unit.target: O nome da propriedade representada pelo <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the object (of a class that is derived from <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />) that represents the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o objeto (de uma classe derivada de <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />) que representa a propriedade especificada.

trans-unit.source: An object of a class that is derived from the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto de uma classe derivada do <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />.

trans-unit.source: The `attribName` must be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: O `attribName` devem ser digitados exatamente como o nome de alguma propriedade específica de um objeto do sistema de impressão, incluindo maiusculas e minúsculas.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePort%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "QueuePort", not "PrintPort", "Port", or "Queueport".
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePort%2A> propriedade de um <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> objeto deve ser escrito "QueuePort", não "PrintPort", "Port" ou "Queueport".

trans-unit.source: The source of the event.
trans-unit.target: A fonte do evento.

trans-unit.source: Implements the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable" /> interface and raises the deserialization event when the deserialization is complete.
trans-unit.target: Implementa a interface <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable" /> e gera o evento de desserialização quando a desserialização for concluída.

trans-unit.source: The name of the attribute.
trans-unit.target: O nome do atributo.

trans-unit.source: An object of a type that is derived from <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto de um tipo derivada de <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />.

trans-unit.source: Sets the value of the specified attribute to an object of a class that is derived from <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />.
trans-unit.target: Define o valor do atributo especificado como um objeto de uma classe derivada de <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty" />.

trans-unit.source: If the dictionary does not already contain `attribName`, `attribName` will be added and set to `attribValue`, provided that `attribName` is identical to `attribValue`.Name.
trans-unit.target: Se o dicionário ainda não contiver `attribName`, `attribName` será adicionada e definida como `attribValue`, desde que `attribName` é idêntico ao `attribValue`. Nome.

trans-unit.source: If these values are not identical, this method does nothing.
trans-unit.target: Se esses valores não são idênticos, esse método não fará nada.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to use this method to install a second printer that differs in its properties from an existing printer only in location, port, and shared status.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir mostra como usar esse método para instalar uma segunda impressora que difere em suas propriedades de uma impressora existente apenas no local, porta e status compartilhado.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="attribName" /> is already in the dictionary and it already has the value <paramref name="attribValue" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="attribName" /> já está no dicionário e já tem o valor <paramref name="attribValue" />.
